Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:07.32,Main,Obo,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I must tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.31,0:00:10.58,Main,Obo,0000,0000,0000,,Just what Yoshida Shoyo...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:12.83,Main,Obo,0000,0000,0000,,What Utsuro is.
